168
00:10:40,302 --> 00:10:41,835
OH.

169
00:10:41,868 --> 00:10:44,102
THANK YOU.

170
00:10:46,202 --> 00:10:48,168
TEACHER.

171
00:10:48,202 --> 00:10:51,335
