178
00:11:07,202 --> 00:11:10,235
- SURE. WHY NOT?
- [ SIGHS ]

179
00:11:11,635 --> 00:11:13,635
I'M OKAY WITH THAT.

180
00:11:17,335 --> 00:11:20,668
I'M SORRY.
I WAS EVEN WEIRDER BACK THEN
THAN I AM NOW.

181
00:11:20,702 --> 00:11:25,002
IT'S JUST-- THERE YOU WERE,
THIS AMAZING PERSON,
AND I REALLY LOOKED UP TO YOU.

182
00:11:25,035 --> 00:11:28,535
WELL, AMAZING MIGHT BE GOING
A BIT TOO FAR.

183
00:11:28,568 --> 00:11:31,535
- HUH?
