I WANTED TO BE.

189
00:11:45,835 --> 00:11:47,635
I LOOKED UP TO HIM.

190
00:11:48,802 --> 00:11:51,468
HE'S SWEET.
I CAN SEE WHY YOU WOULD.

191
00:11:51,502 --> 00:11:54,035
YOU'RE RIGHT. HE IS.

192
00:11:54,068 --> 00:11:56,602
BUT AT SOME POINT,
WE ALL HAVE TO GROW UP,
DON'T WE?

193
00:11:58,102 --> 00:12:00,868
YOU WORKED HARD
TO GET THIS FAR, SHIEMI.

194
00:12:00,902 --> 00:12:02,435
YOU'VE CHANGED A LOT.

195
00:12:02,468 --> 00:12:05,068
BUT IF YOU WANT
TO KEEP ATTENDING CLASSES
AT THE CRAM SCHOOL,

196
00:12:05,102 --> 00:12:07,502
YOU HAVE TO MAKE A DECISION.

197
00:12:07,535 --> 00:12:12,002
SHIEMI, EVERYONE KNOWS
YOU HAVE THE POTENTIAL
TO BECOME A TAMER.

198
00:12:12,035 --> 00:12:14,868
