TO REALLY THINK ABOUT.

199
00:12:14,902 --> 00:12:18,235
TALK TO YOUR MOTHER FIRST,
AND LET ME KNOW WHAT YOUR
DECISION IS BY TOMORROW.

200
00:12:18,268 --> 00:12:21,502
- I HAVE TO TALK
TO MY MOM?
- YOU SHOULD.

201
00:12:21,535 --> 00:12:23,135
IF YOU BECOME AN EXWIRE,

202
00:12:23,168 --> 00:12:26,602
YOU'LL HAVE TO BE PREPARED
TO FACE LIFE-OR-DEATH
SITUATIONS.

203
00:12:26,635 --> 00:12:28,202
