FOR THAT.

204
00:12:29,468 --> 00:12:31,335
YEAH, THAT FIGURES.

205
00:12:31,368 --> 00:12:34,435
DURING THE EXAM I WASN'T SO SURE
I WAS EVEN GOING TO MAKE IT.

206
00:12:34,468 --> 00:12:38,235
RIGHT. I KNOW
THAT MUST HAVE BEEN
A GRUELING EXPERIENCE FOR YOU.

207
00:12:38,268 --> 00:12:40,602
BUT IT WAS ONLY A TEST,
AFTER ALL.

208
00:12:40,635 --> 00:12:43,635
