YOUR SAFETY IN MIND.

212
00:12:51,168 --> 00:12:53,568
I'M NOT REALLY GOING
TO KILL YOUR BROTHER.

213
00:12:53,602 --> 00:12:54,635
[ GASPS ]

214
00:12:57,002 --> 00:12:59,202
EXCUSE ME.
I HAVE TO GO NOW.

215
00:12:59,235 --> 00:13:01,202
BUT, YUKI--

216
00:13:01,235 --> 00:13:03,402
I'VE GOT A BAD FEELING
ABOUT THIS.

217
00:13:03,435 --> 00:13:05,968
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

218
00:13:16,629 --> 00:13:19,563
[ CRICKETS CHIRPING ]
[ SNORING ]

219
00:13:22,296 --> 00:13:23,796
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

220
00:13:48,963 --> 00:13:51,296
[ GASPS, SIGHS ]

221
00:13:55,084 --> 00:13:56,684
[ GUN COCKS ]

222
00:13:56,717 --> 00:13:59,950
I THOUGHT YOU SAID
YOU WEREN'T GOING
TO KILL HIM,

223
00:13:59,984 --> 00:14:01,984
MR. NOIHAUS.

224
00:14:02,017 --> 00:14:04,484
WELL PLAYED, YUKIO OKUMURA.

225
00:14:04,517 --> 00:14:07,050
RIN?
[ YELLS ]

226
00:14:07,084 --> 00:14:09,984
SHIEMI! WHAT ARE YOU DOING
IN MY ROOM?

227
00:14:10,017 --> 00:14:11,817
NOT THAT I MIND
OR ANYTHING.

228
00:14:11,850 --> 00:14:13,984
SHH. WE'RE NOT IN YOUR ROOM.

229
00:14:14,017 --> 00:14:16,217
YOU WOULDN'T WAKE UP,
SO YUKI BROUGHT YOU HERE.

230
00:14:16,250 --> 00:14:18,850
HE SAID TO LET YOU SLEEP,
BUT I HEARD SOMETHING.

231
00:14:18,884 --> 00:14:21,684
- [ TWO GUNSHOTS ]
- [ BOTH GASP ]

232
00:14:22,917 --> 00:14:24,584
COME FORTH!

233
00:14:36,250 --> 00:14:40,117
NOIHAUS, WHY ARE YOU TRYING
TO KILL MY BROTHER?

234
00:14:52,684 --> 00:14:55,084
[ GRUNTING ]

235
00:15:02,246 --> 00:15:03,979
YOU'RE SLOW.

236
00:15:04,012 --> 00:15:08,946
FROM A CORPSE IN THE GROUND
WHERE VULTURES
WON'T GATHER ROUND, ARISE.

237
00:15:08,979 --> 00:15:12,679
[ LAUGHS ]
YOU'RE ABOUT TO MEET
THE HIGHEST RANKING NABERIUS...

238
00:15:12,712 --> 00:15:14,312
AMONGST ALL MY PAWNS.

239
00:15:17,612 --> 00:15:20,312
[ ROARING ]

240
00:15:26,179 --> 00:15:29,146
[ LAUGHING ]

241
00:15:29,179 --> 00:15:31,912
[ YUKIO ]
I HAVE TO BREAK
THE MAGIC CIRCLE.

242
00:15:40,712 --> 00:15:42,679
[ GRUNTS ]

243
00:15:42,712 --> 00:15:45,379
[ GROWLING ]

244
00:15:50,746 --> 00:15:53,212
[ ROARING ]

245
00:15:55,812 --> 00:15:59,046
DAMN YOU!
I KNEW IT!

246
00:15:59,079 --> 00:16:01,346
- YOU CURSED DEMON!
- [ RIN SHOUTING ]

247
00:16:03,512 --> 00:16:08,346
[ LAUGHS ]
YOU LOOK HUMAN, BUT HOLY WATER
WORKS ON YOU LIKE ALL DEMONS.

248
00:16:08,379 --> 00:16:12,012
YOU CAN'T HIDE YOUR NATURE,
EVEN WITH THE SKIN
YOU'RE WEARING.

249
00:16:12,046 --> 00:16:14,612
HOLY WATER?
WHAT THE HELL?

250
00:16:16,646 --> 00:16:18,879
[ SHOUTING ]

251
00:16:18,912 --> 00:16:20,512
[ SCREAMING ]

252
00:16:22,446 --> 00:16:25,179
[ LAUGHS ]

253
00:16:27,446 --> 00:16:28,712
WHAT THE--

254
00:16:29,846 --> 00:16:31,712
[ PANTING ]

255
00:16:33,846 --> 00:16:36,346
DAMN. HE BROKE THE CIRCLE.

256
00:16:42,846 --> 00:16:46,546
NOIHAUS, FOR YOUR OWN GOOD,
YOU'D BETTER STOP THIS NOW.

257
00:16:46,579 --> 00:16:49,612
IF YOU LOSE ANY MORE BLOOD,
YOU'LL DIE.

258
00:16:49,646 --> 00:16:52,179
WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU?

259
00:16:55,212 --> 00:16:58,246
WHAT AM I?
A SURVIVOR OF THE BLUE NIGHT.

260
00:16:58,279 --> 00:17:00,879
THE BLUE NIGHT?

261
00:17:00,912 --> 00:17:05,246
HERE'S WHAT HAPPENED.
SIXTEEN YEARS AGO SATAN CROSSED
THE BARRIER TO OUR WORLD...

262
00:17:05,279 --> 00:17:07,179
AND MASSACRED
ALL THE TOP CLERGYMEN.

263
00:17:07,212 --> 00:17:08,746
WE'VE CALLED IT
THE BLUE NIGHT EVER SINCE.

264
00:17:10,046 --> 00:17:11,879
YOU DON'T SAY?

265
00:17:13,279 --> 00:17:15,446
IT LASTED A FEW SECONDS.

266
00:17:15,479 --> 00:17:17,546
MY BODY WAS POSSESSED
BY SATAN,

267
00:17:17,579 --> 00:17:20,646
AND I LOST THIS.

268
00:17:20,679 --> 00:17:24,012
MY EYE. THERE WAS NOTHING
I COULD DO TO STOP IT.

269
00:17:24,046 --> 00:17:26,646
AND WHEN MY FAMILY
TRIED TO SAVE ME,

270
00:17:26,679 --> 00:17:30,446
SATAN TOOK OVER MY HAND
AND USED IT TO SLAUGHTER
THEM ALL.

271
00:17:32,279 --> 00:17:34,412
I WON'T FORGIVE SATAN...

272
00:17:34,446 --> 00:17:37,312
OR ANY DEMON
I COME ACROSS.

273
00:17:37,346 --> 00:17:41,146
AND THAT GOES FOR THE SON
OF SATAN AS WELL!

274
00:17:41,179 --> 00:17:43,946
I'M GOING TO KILL YOU,

275
00:17:43,979 --> 00:17:46,312
EVEN IF IT MEANS I DIE DOING IT!

276
00:17:49,612 --> 00:17:51,279
[ GROANING ]

277
00:17:55,179 --> 00:17:57,346
DID THAT MAKE YOU FEEL
ANY BETTER?

278
00:17:59,679 --> 00:18:00,746
RIN!

279
00:18:02,379 --> 00:18:06,646
IF YOU THINK
YOU'RE STILL NOT SATISFIED,
I CAN HANDLE MORE.

280
00:18:06,679 --> 00:18:08,212
I'M USED TO IT.

281
00:18:08,246 --> 00:18:11,512
PICK THE TIME,
AND I'LL BE THERE
WAITING FOR YOU.

282
00:18:12,946 --> 00:18:15,412
BUT YOU GOTTA PROMISE ME...

283
00:18:15,446 --> 00:18:18,546
THAT YOU WON'T DRAG
INNOCENT PEOPLE INTO IT AGAIN.

284
00:18:18,579 --> 00:18:20,279
[ GASPS ]

285
00:18:24,112 --> 00:18:26,746
DON'T THINK FOR A SECOND
THAT IT'S OVER.

286
00:18:29,379 --> 00:18:33,679
I'M NOT THE ONLY ONE
THAT'D LOVE TO SEE YOU DIE.

287
00:18:33,712 --> 00:18:35,846
GET READY FOR WHAT'S COMING.

288
00:18:43,746 --> 00:18:45,412
[ PANTING ]

289
00:18:48,179 --> 00:18:50,412
[ PANTING ]
NEE?

290
00:18:50,446 --> 00:18:52,312
YUKI? RIN?

291
00:18:53,946 --> 00:18:56,746
MR. NOIHAUS.

292
00:18:56,779 --> 00:18:59,112
WHAT HAPPENED?

293
00:18:59,146 --> 00:19:01,779
JUST LEAVE ME ALONE.

294
00:19:10,046 --> 00:19:12,146
IT'S ALREADY STARTING
TO CLOSE UP.

295
00:19:13,412 --> 00:19:16,312
YOU KNOW ME.
I ALWAYS HEALED UP PRETTY QUICK.

296
00:19:16,346 --> 00:19:18,879
I GUESS THAT MEANS
I REALLY AM A MONSTER.

297
00:19:20,546 --> 00:19:21,812
[ DOOR BANGS ]

298
00:19:21,846 --> 00:19:23,612
[ SHIEMI ]
YUKI! RIN!

299
00:19:23,646 --> 00:19:25,946
SHIEMI.

300
00:19:25,979 --> 00:19:28,546
R-RIN! WHAT HAPPENED?

301
00:19:28,579 --> 00:19:29,812
[ GASPS ]

302
00:19:29,846 --> 00:19:31,379
UH, NOTHING.
I'M FINE.

303
00:19:31,412 --> 00:19:33,212
THAT'S A GHOUL
TEMPTAINT!

304
00:19:33,246 --> 00:19:34,879
I HAVE TO TREAT IT.

305
00:19:34,912 --> 00:19:37,646
NO. I'M OKAY.
NO, YOU'RE NOT.

306
00:19:37,679 --> 00:19:40,812
NO ARGUMENTS.
LIE DOWN
AND TRY TO STAY CALM.

307
00:19:40,846 --> 00:19:42,312
HUH?
I SAID LIE DOWN!

308
00:19:42,346 --> 00:19:45,412
NEE, MAY I HAVE
SOME MR. SANCHO?
NEE!

309
00:19:48,046 --> 00:19:50,579
[ CHUCKLES ]
THAT'S GREAT, THANKS.

310
00:19:50,612 --> 00:19:53,679
YEAH, I THINK IT'S WORKING.
I FEEL WAY BETTER NOW.

311
00:19:57,112 --> 00:19:59,846
RIN, I'VE DECIDED.
HUH?

312
00:20:02,312 --> 00:20:04,546
I'VE DECIDED.
OKAY. WHAT'D YOU DECIDE?

313
00:20:10,279 --> 00:20:15,079
RIN, YOU WERE
ALWAYS ABLE TO DO
THE THINGS I COULDN'T.

314
00:20:15,112 --> 00:20:18,379
OH, WELL. GUESS
I'LL NEVER BE A MATCH FOR HIM.

315
00:20:20,146 --> 00:20:23,479
EINS, ZWEI, DREI.

316
00:20:23,512 --> 00:20:26,212
CONGRATULATIONS
ON PASSING THE EXAM!

317
00:20:26,246 --> 00:20:28,346
YOU'VE ALL BEEN PROMOTED
TO BECOME EXWIRES.

318
00:20:28,379 --> 00:20:30,312
[ CHEERING ]
ALL RIGHT!

319
00:20:30,346 --> 00:20:32,546
- THANK GOODNESS.
- [ LAUGHS ]

320
00:20:32,579 --> 00:20:37,046
AND TO CELEBRATE,
I'M TREATING YOU ALL TO A FEAST.

321
00:20:37,079 --> 00:20:39,546
WHO'S HUNGRY FOR MONJA?

322
00:20:39,579 --> 00:20:40,979
[ ALL ]
WHAT?

323
00:20:41,012 --> 00:20:43,246
MONJA?
BARBECUE'S WAY BETTER.

324
00:20:44,812 --> 00:20:46,846
[ RIN ]
SO YOU'RE GONNA BE
AN EXORCIST, HUH?

325
00:20:48,579 --> 00:20:51,112
YEP. I'M GONNA HELP
EVERYONE OUT.

326
00:20:51,146 --> 00:20:53,046
UH, YOU GONNA BE OKAY
FIGHTING?

327
00:20:53,079 --> 00:20:55,979
OF COURSE I'LL BE OKAY.
REALLY?

328
00:20:56,012 --> 00:21:00,279
I MUST APOLOGIZE
FOR MR. NOIHAUS'S
RECENT BEHAVIOR.

329
00:21:00,312 --> 00:21:05,246
BELIEVE ME, I NEVER DREAMED
HE'D LET HIS PERSONAL FEELINGS
INTERFERE IN SUCH A WAY.

330
00:21:05,279 --> 00:21:08,212
I'LL MAKE SURE SUCH A THING
NEVER HAPPENS AGAIN.

331
00:21:11,246 --> 00:21:13,179
I'D APPRECIATE IT.

332
00:21:14,912 --> 00:21:16,379
[ SHIMA ]
HEY, MR. OKUMURA,

333
00:21:16,412 --> 00:21:18,212
WOULD YOU LIKE
SOME RAMUNE?

334
00:21:18,246 --> 00:21:20,279
YES, PLEASE.
THANK YOU.

335
00:21:24,279 --> 00:21:26,112
[ LINE RINGING ]

336
00:21:26,146 --> 00:21:28,379
GUESS WHO.
<i>[ AMAIMON ]</i>
<i>YES?</i>

337
00:21:28,412 --> 00:21:30,146
NOIHAUS FOLLOWED MY ORDERS.

338
00:21:30,179 --> 00:21:33,946
HOWEVER, WHEN IT CAME
TO FINISHING THE TASK,
HE CAME UP SHORT.

339
00:21:33,979 --> 00:21:36,946
COME TO TRUE CROSS ACADEMY
RIGHT AWAY.

340
00:21:36,979 --> 00:21:40,879
BUT YOUR PROTECTIVE BARRIER
PREVENTS ME FROM ENTERING,
BIG BROTHER.

341
00:21:40,912 --> 00:21:43,279
I'LL HAVE NOIHAUS GUIDE YOU.

342
00:21:43,312 --> 00:21:45,279
WE'LL DISCUSS
THE DETAILS LATER.

343
00:21:45,312 --> 00:21:48,146
UNDERSTOOD?
ROGER THAT.

344
00:21:48,179 --> 00:21:50,079
[ SUGURO ]
IT LOOKS LIKE IT'S DONE.
[ GASPS ]

345
00:21:50,112 --> 00:21:52,412
[ RIN LAUGHS ]
I'M DIGGING IN!

346
00:21:52,446 --> 00:21:54,979
HOLD IT, KIDDIES!
DON'T START WITHOUT ME!

347
00:21:55,012 --> 00:21:57,946
[ BEEPING ]

348
00:21:57,979 --> 00:21:59,479
[ SIGHS ]

349
00:21:59,512 --> 00:22:02,579
MY FATHER AND BROTHER
ARE SO OBSESSED
WITH THIS RIN OKUMURA.

350
00:22:02,612 --> 00:22:05,146
I WONDER IF HE'S
REALLY THAT SPECIAL.

351
00:22:05,179 --> 00:22:08,579
I HOPE HE CAN ENTERTAIN ME
FOR A LITTLE WHILE.

352
00:22:11,612 --> 00:22:14,612
♪ [ MAN SINGING IN JAPANESE ]

353
00:23:38,512 --> 00:23:42,846
[ RIN LAUGHING ]
GONNA SCOOP IT ALL UP!

354
00:23:42,879 --> 00:23:44,912
NO, PLEASE!
YOU CAN'T TAKE THAT ONE!

355
00:23:44,946 --> 00:23:49,646
THE CHEESE-BACON-MOCHI MONJA
IS ONE OF MY TOP THREE
MONJA MUNCHIES EVER!

356
00:23:49,679 --> 00:23:52,346
I DON'T CARE IF YOU'RE
THE DIRECTOR OF THE ACADEMY.

357
00:23:52,379 --> 00:23:54,879
WHEN IT COMES TO EATING,
IT'S FIRST COME, FIRST SERVED.

358
00:23:54,912 --> 00:23:58,312
[ WHINING ]

359
00:23:58,346 --> 00:24:00,346
YOU LITTLE DEMON!

360
00:24:02,946 --> 00:24:04,746
[ RIN ]
ARE YOU GONNA KILL HIM?

361
00:24:04,779 --> 00:24:07,112
[ YUKIO ]
THIS SCHOOL DOESN'T HAVE
AN EXORCIST ON THE FACULTY...

362
00:24:07,146 --> 00:24:09,146
WHO CAN TAME A DEMON
OF THAT CLASS.

363
00:24:09,179 --> 00:24:12,779
[ RIN ]
MY FATHER'S DEAD.
SHIRO'S DEAD.

364
00:24:12,812 --> 00:24:15,346
YOU ARE ALL LIARS!

